Many people are of the opinion that the colour for Valentine is red and white, while you see most people gallivanting around in this colour on Val’s day, there are different colours you can try out for your Valentine dates. Below are some colours that can be worn depending on the kind of date you are going for: Concert Image Fashion Lifestyle Community If you get a ticket to go to a concert with the love of your life or your Val date, you do not have to do a red and white. You can go in a jean pant with a white top or a bum short with a big top. Also for men, you can wear your long jean or three-quarter pants with any top to go with it. Date night
