Yes, it is Valentine, don’t wear that old short and top, change into something appealing. As a man, don’t just wear boxers and singlet; wear something that will prove to your lover how intentional you are about spending the day with them. You can cook together, Netflix and chill together, dance together, do things that will remind you of how lucky you are to be in each other’s life.